canonical:
  title: 書情
  author: 金克己
  language: lzh
  text: 晚年佐邑竟何成唯有千篇寫客情邊吏不知詩有味幾回相咲絶冠纓鳥散楊花落屋除樓頭一榻黑甜餘家童火急供紈扇正是炎風用事初
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 書情
  author: 金克己
  language: lzh
  text: 晚年佐邑竟何成。唯有千篇寫客情。邊吏不知詩有味。幾回相咲絶冠纓。鳥散楊花落屋除。樓頭一榻黑甜餘。家童火急供紈扇。正是炎風用事初。
korean:
  title: 서정
  author: 김극기
  language: kor
  text: |-
    늘그막에 고을에 속관 되어 무엇을 이루었노
    오직 천 편의 시로써 객정을 읊었네
    변방의 아전들이 시의 맛을 몰라서
    몇 번이고 서로 웃어 갓끈이 끊어졌네
    새가 버들꽃을 흩어 지붕에 휘날리니
    다락 머리 평상 위에 낮잠 잔 나머질세
    아이놈은 불현듯이 부채질해 주나니
    정히 뜨거운 여름이 용사할 처음일세
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0220_020_0780&viewSync=OT
  footnotes:
  - key: '[주-D001] 몇 번이고 …… 끊어졌네 : '
    value: 하늘을 우러러 크게 웃으니 갓끈이 끊어졌다. 《史記》
english:
  title: On Sentiment
  author: Kim Geuk-gi
  language: eng
  text: |-
    In my declining years, what have I achieved as a minor official in this remote county?
    Only through a thousand poems have I given voice to a wanderer's heart.
    The local clerks know nothing of poetry's subtle grace—
    How many times we've laughed together till the cords of our caps snapped clean.

    Birds scatter, willow catkins drift and fall upon the eaves.
    Upstairs on my cot, the sweet remnants of an afternoon nap still linger.
    The boy hastily waves the silk fan for me—
    For this is precisely when the blazing summer first asserts its reign.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: The image of the cap cord snapping from laughter echoes a passage from the Records of the Grand Historian, suggesting unrestrained, liberating laughter amid humble circumstances.
